Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:01.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,683)\bord0}「20年前」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.15,0:00:06.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和优子是小时候在教会的福利院里相遇的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.98,0:00:10.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里有许多失去父母的小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.64,0:00:13.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和优子都是其中之一
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.81,0:00:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一天 优子不知被领养到哪里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.63,0:00:21.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自那之后我一直呆在福利院里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.23,0:00:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和优子的关系 仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.83,0:00:26.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1507,813)\bord0}仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.70,0:00:45.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.73,0:02:27.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又回想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.46,0:02:44.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 走过路过不要错过
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.32,0:02:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然现在或许不合时宜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.84,0:02:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这件毛衣 和别处的便宜货可不一样哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.66,0:02:52.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么不一样了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.38,0:02:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 火村 要买这件毛衣吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.10,0:02:58.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你穿过的谁要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.00,0:03:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这么绝情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.02,0:03:04.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是可以不来学校了么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.54,0:03:07.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有许多事情需要处理啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.71,0:03:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.63,0:03:10.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个已经作为最优先事项处理完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.92,0:03:12.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这做法真像是你的作风
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.21,0:03:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个多少钱？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.06,0:03:18.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦哦 真有眼光啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.66,0:03:19.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是送给男朋友的？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.23,0:03:23.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定是呢 你说呢 火村前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.96,0:03:46.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火村前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.36,0:03:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.66,0:03:51.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事情就不能打招呼了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.82,0:03:54.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经忘了么 我应该说过别靠近我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.18,0:03:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记得哦 很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.31,0:03:58.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.37,0:04:00.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么是火村前辈的自由
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.57,0:04:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 做什么也是我的自由哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.69,0:04:10.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微陪我一下可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.72,0:04:22.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优子 你不是说天文部已经被废部了么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.91,0:04:23.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.90,0:04:26.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那为什么会有屋顶的钥匙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.92,0:04:28.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该已经不外借了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.95,0:04:32.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不很起眼 但也是一个很有历史的社团呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.21,0:04:35.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前或许有个坏坏的前辈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.43,0:04:38.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擅自配的钥匙么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.45,0:04:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代代相传的钥匙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.17,0:04:43.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,废部那时 便由我收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.44,0:04:48.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微出点轨 学校生活才会充满乐趣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.36,0:04:53.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 平静的学校生活才是我心所向
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.46,0:04:55.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀 真是成熟呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.20,0:04:58.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不能惹是生非
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.97,0:05:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火村前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.20,0:05:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.16,0:05:05.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我离开福利院之后的事情 能说给我听听吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.98,0:05:07.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说这些干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.94,0:05:10.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之后我一直在福利院中生活
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.22,0:05:14.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考上音羽那天起 便独立了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.54,0:05:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.98,0:05:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在福利院中…吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.56,0:05:21.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有人想不开去收留我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.16,0:05:23.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.34,0:05:28.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在努力 为了能尽早独立生活
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.72,0:05:31.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 音羽的学费不便宜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.25,0:05:35.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特待生 入学金与学费免除
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.35,0:05:37.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想自找麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.12,0:05:42.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了能自存于世 我也付出了许许多多
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.71,0:05:44.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了 优子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.10,0:05:45.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.04,0:05:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再说一次 别靠近我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.98,0:05:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要让我再回想起那个时侯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.23,0:05:56.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明忘了就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.27,0:06:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茜的手表 忘了就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.27,0:06:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0400,0000,,{\3c&H0000FF\fs56}红色的手表
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.92,0:06:03.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你会知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.32,0:06:07.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然…还在做那个梦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.09,0:06:10.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1640,1037)\bord0}「这」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.95,0:06:28.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是时候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.92,0:06:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 久濑先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.91,0:06:33.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 瑞希
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.40,0:06:39.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样真的好吗 不去些什么地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.31,0:06:45.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得到了国外 不做一些特别的事情不是很可惜吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.66,0:06:49.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是国外 跟日本的音羽城不是一样吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.09,0:06:51.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 说得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.61,0:06:55.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且和久濑先生一起洗衣服 可是很特别的事情哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.28,0:06:57.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这难得的假日？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.08,0:07:00.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我来说每一天都很特别
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.81,0:07:02.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是不是假日
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.84,0:07:03.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是乐观呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.30,0:07:07.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这么想比较有乐趣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.88,0:07:12.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 久濑先生 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.18,0:07:14.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 莲治
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.60,0:07:16.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,复习应考还顺利吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.67,0:07:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙 非常不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.06,0:07:21.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛 算了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.56,0:07:23.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不经历风雨 怎能见彩虹嘛 少年
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.91,0:07:25.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 莲治
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.29,0:07:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来洗衣服了 要洗的都拿出来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.05,0:07:30.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了 我自己会洗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.77,0:07:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正一样要洗 拿出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.00,0:07:36.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了啦 现在学习都弄得脑袋胀死了 别管了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.97,0:07:40.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.12,0:07:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说的话就算倾尽全力也要抢过来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.82,0:07:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？啊 等等 瑞希…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.54,0:07:51.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了 交出来 脱得爽快点…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.51,0:07:56.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的…别乱来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.04,0:07:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那条浴巾算什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.23,0:08:01.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留下一件不洗可不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.30,0:08:02.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个也交出来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.57,0:08:04.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饶了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.88,0:08:08.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 又不是什么黄花闺女
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.03,0:08:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都这年纪了还有什么好害羞的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.28,0:08:12.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懵懂年华啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.52,0:08:15.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我该帮些什么忙呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.74,0:08:18.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮我把有颜色的衣物分出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.95,0:08:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菫女士的内衣是哪个呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.36,0:08:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚已经拿出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.04,0:08:26.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我到底来干什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.25,0:08:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗衣物的乐趣在于晾干的时候哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.29,0:08:35.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将床单啪一下展开 水珠四溅的味道很好闻呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.33,0:08:42.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久濑先生是为什么开始拉小提琴的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.97,0:08:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来也是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.51,0:08:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs60}约翰·梅尔策(Johann Mälzel)：节拍器的改进者 这里以“约翰·梅尔策的女儿”指代节拍器
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.51,0:08:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,契机大概是在音乐室里邂逅约翰·梅尔策的女儿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.93,0:08:50.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约翰·梅尔策的女儿？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.90,0:08:53.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她性格内向 做事异常认真
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.06,0:08:56.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是无论对谁都一视同仁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.01,0:08:58.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我的初恋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.43,0:09:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她教会了我很多事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.27,0:09:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正义 秩序 世间的险恶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.17,0:09:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于 我知道了她出生于1815年
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.51,0:09:15.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1815年…那不是将近两百年前吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.64,0:09:17.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是你的音乐老师什么的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.45,0:09:20.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我来说 现在也是老师哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.24,0:09:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的名字叫「节拍器」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.24,0:09:23.98,*Default,NTP,0386,0000,0000,,{\fs55.5}Metronome
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.92,0:09:30.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.37,0:09:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生气了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.21,0:09:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你希望我生气吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.89,0:09:37.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑞希微现愠色的样子更显可爱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.54,0:09:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗 洗衣机停了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.04,0:09:44.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我我我去晾衣服 请帮一下忙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.22,0:09:56.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久濑先生 久濑先生 怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.42,0:09:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救护车救护车
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.61,0:10:03.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 怎么会不通的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.95,0:10:01.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Banner;1;0;100,{\an8\fs60\3c&H6000FF}澳大利亚的紧急求救号码是000哟XD
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.13,0:10:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菫女士…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.49,0:10:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是不能就这么放着不管啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.99,0:10:33.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 我也不是故意的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.43,0:10:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算摆好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.05,0:10:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久濑先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.97,0:10:56.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久濑先生 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.47,0:10:59.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要天使朝我微笑的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.78,0:11:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去没事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.35,0:11:03.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.60,0:11:05.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.47,0:11:08.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡不着…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.69,0:11:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.52,0:11:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孤身一人 往往噩梦缠身
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.75,0:11:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 我在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.16,0:11:22.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.32,0:11:25.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1633,1037)\bord0}「往」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.76,0:11:32.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀 怎么了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.21,0:11:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久濑先生 醒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.64,0:11:37.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑞希 我睡着了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.24,0:11:39.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 睡了很久
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.36,0:11:46.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 瑞希 一天就这样浪费了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.93,0:11:51.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 偶尔如此悠哉游哉一天也不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.17,0:11:54.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天会连今天的份 一起补偿你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.17,0:11:56.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.42,0:12:01.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.32,0:12:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.52,0:12:17.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.35,0:12:20.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与甜蜜回忆诀别
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.93,0:12:23.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交往过的女朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.94,0:12:25.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收信人不明退回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.29,0:12:28.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经搬走了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.21,0:12:29.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样好么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.32,0:12:32.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有别的选择吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.72,0:12:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本以为全部解决了的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.15,0:12:36.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会退回来呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.26,0:12:39.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是又要让我回想到那些日子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.83,0:12:42.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且偏偏又是在这种时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.21,0:12:44.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种时候？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.32,0:12:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.47,0:12:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退回来的 不仅仅是女朋友的信么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.35,0:12:53.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明麻烦的人际关系全都处理掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.74,0:12:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么事到如今还…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.51,0:12:56.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 稀罕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.18,0:12:58.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,广野凪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.80,0:12:59.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知她还好不
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.27,0:13:01.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.77,0:13:03.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管它呢 随便了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.37,0:13:07.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 今后打算怎么做？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.24,0:13:10.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那还用说么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.18,0:13:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部抛弃 仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.27,0:13:33.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茜…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.05,0:13:37.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.17,0:13:41.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.62,0:13:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茜？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.69,0:13:47.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.29,0:13:52.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.82,0:13:56.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.11,0:14:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,画得真好呢 夕哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.72,0:14:07.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别叫我哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.69,0:14:08.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.86,0:14:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.25,0:14:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是你的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.13,0:14:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那应该叫什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.46,0:14:16.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁管你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.36,0:14:19.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 夕君…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.13,0:14:24.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕君 喜欢画画？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.66,0:14:25.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.16,0:14:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕君很拿手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.01,0:14:29.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.42,0:14:30.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.06,0:14:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕君
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.15,0:14:34.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.87,0:14:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.47,0:14:44.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕君 下次画优子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.23,0:14:44.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.96,0:14:45.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,画嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.17,0:14:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你没办法…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.42,0:14:55.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 夕君
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.38,0:14:57.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.62,0:14:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.91,0:15:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太浪费纸了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.35,0:15:02.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好过分 夕君小气鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.04,0:15:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的没纸了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.19,0:15:06.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.96,0:15:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.45,0:15:10.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 这次怎么这么轻易就放弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.89,0:15:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为补偿 夕君画的画都要给优子看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.49,0:15:18.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕君想画的 我都想看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.75,0:15:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.40,0:16:02.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕君
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.52,0:16:03.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.46,0:16:07.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕君 想要妹妹吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.11,0:16:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想要个妹妹吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.29,0:16:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要问这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.62,0:16:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何都想知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.25,0:16:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕君…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.46,0:16:23.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕君？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.89,0:16:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.45,0:16:29.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经不要妹妹了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.06,0:16:32.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经不要那样了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.91,0:16:35.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.15,0:16:36.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别叫我哥哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.36,0:16:40.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的妹妹…已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.53,0:16:45.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.46,0:16:55.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那几天之后 优子被远房亲戚所领养 离开了福利院
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.72,0:17:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人终难免沦落到形孤影只
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.86,0:17:20.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论骨肉至亲抑或葭莩远戚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.64,0:17:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终有一日会云树遥隔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.78,0:17:28.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我对他人不抱期待
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.84,0:17:32.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我对他人不加干涉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.85,0:17:38.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我拥有了不依赖他人而活下去的能力…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.02,0:17:52.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你 却为何一直紧追我不舍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.25,0:17:54.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.68,0:18:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈 我很高兴能与前辈相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.86,0:18:02.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道为什么吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.52,0:18:03.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.63,0:18:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈真迟钝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.65,0:18:07.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是一点没变
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.30,0:18:09.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来找茬的么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.10,0:18:11.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没办法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.20,0:18:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.41,0:18:19.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火村前辈 你是我的初恋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.51,0:18:24.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我的初恋 还没有结束哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.61,0:18:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕君
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.86,0:18:32.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就让我来让你忘却
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.42,0:18:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就让我来抹却你那悲伤的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.60,0:18:59.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心率60
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.16,0:19:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正常值
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.58,0:19:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MM60
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.05,0:19:05.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0095,,{\fs60}Lengo
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.05,0:19:05.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢板
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.73,0:19:13.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正常 同步率无异常
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.87,0:19:15.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,节律缓慢而平稳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.16,0:19:22.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久濑君 刚才那下慢了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.07,0:19:24.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不成样子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.16,0:19:28.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的节拍器真的是音乐家的心脏么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.45,0:19:33.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的心脏真的是音乐家的节拍器么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.76,0:19:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗒 嗒 嗒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.09,0:19:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咚 咚 咚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.56,0:19:40.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发条马上就要松了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.96,0:19:42.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松了的发条由谁来上？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.15,0:19:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗒 嗒 嗒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.54,0:19:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咚 咚 咚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.70,0:19:50.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刻画的节律是 那所剩的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.18,0:19:55.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久濑先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.07,0:20:00.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑞希 这么晚怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.12,0:20:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些睡不着 出来乘凉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.28,0:20:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.05,0:20:07.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 久濑先生 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.07,0:20:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说修好了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.62,0:20:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修理？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.45,0:20:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 还不行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.41,0:20:20.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛 真可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.55,0:20:22.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 已经不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.40,0:20:28.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听了久濑先生给我的CD
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.22,0:20:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说至今为止没怎么听过古典乐 但真觉得很厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.75,0:20:36.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宁静的曲子让人舒心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.71,0:20:39.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有的曲子突然激昂直上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.83,0:20:42.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,震撼到我了 真是太帅了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.28,0:20:43.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直上？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.48,0:20:45.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 最让人吃惊的是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.52,0:20:49.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古典乐竟是如此妖艳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.96,0:20:50.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖艳…？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.48,0:20:55.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明没有歌词 却仿若有人在耳边喃喃低语
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.53,0:21:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「喜欢你」 就好像被如此诉说着 让人心跳不已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.73,0:21:07.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有许多名曲是在恋爱或失恋的时候诞生的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.37,0:21:14.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想到这里 就有些在意能做出让人如此遐想的演奏的久濑先生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.77,0:21:17.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久濑先生 虽说有些突然
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.03,0:21:18.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.93,0:21:24.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像喜欢上了久濑先生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.86,0:21:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.49,0:21:44.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真头痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.30,0:23:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伪装的是小丑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.29,0:23:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隐藏的是黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.79,0:23:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ef - a tale of melodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.64,0:23:34.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,union
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.40,0:23:37.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你听得见吗？ 那真实的旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.71,0:00:51.04,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,15)\fad(300,300)}Love, I've got to feel it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.97,0:00:54.28,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,15)\fad(300,300)}If you put your trust in me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.27,0:00:57.69,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,15)\fad(300,300)}I know what my life would be
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.54,0:01:02.90,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,15)\fad(300,300)}Oh, you are all I ever need
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.60,0:01:08.57,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,15)\fad(300,300)}I try to hear what you say
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.27,0:01:10.73,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,15)\fad(300,300)}So I pray
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.43,0:01:14.32,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,15)\fad(300,300)}But you're fading away
